     Juliet Alpha Sierra         Yellow Bird


PXH-1 Phoenix Hawk

The Phoenix Hawk is a common, versatile Mech that has become a staple of
Star League Recon Forces.  Its armor is heavy enough to withstand sustained
combat, while its array of lasers makes it a formidable opponent.

Mass: 45 tons
Cruising Speed: 64.8 KPH
Maximum Speed:  97.2 KPH
Jumpjets: 2 Pitban 9000's
Jump Capacity: 180 meters
Armor: Durallex Light
