SHD-2H Shadow Hawk

This medium sized Mech has diverse armament to make it useful in a wide
variety of battle situations.  The Shadow Hawk can handle both long and
short-range engagements with equal facility. While its jump capacity is
limited, its unusual to have any jump capacity at all in a Mech this large.

Mass: 55 tons
Cruising Speed: 54.0 KPH
